    "content": "<h2>Pevné látky</h2>\n<p><strong>Pevné látky</strong> mají stálý tvar i objem. Částice jsou uspořádány těsně vedle sebe a kmitají kolem svých rovnovážných poloh.</p>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;margin:1.5rem auto;max-width:520px;\"><svg viewBox='0 0 500 160' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' style='width:100%;font-family:sans-serif'>\n  <text x='125' y='20' text-anchor='middle' font-weight='bold' fill='#1e40af' font-size='14'>Krystalická</text>\n  <g transform='translate(50,30)'>\n    <circle cx='0' cy='0' r='8' fill='#3b82f6' opacity='0.8'/><circle cx='35' cy='0' r='8' fill='#3b82f6' opacity='0.8'/><circle cx='70' cy='0' r='8' fill='#3b82f6' opacity='0.8'/><circle cx='105' cy='0' r='8' fill='#3b82f6' opacity='0.8'/><circle cx='140' cy='0' r='8' fill='#3b82f6' opacity='0.8'/><circle cx='0' cy='30' r='8' fill='#3b82f6' opacity='0.8'/><circle cx='35' cy='30' r='8' fill='#3b82f6' opacity='0.8'/><circle cx='70' cy='30' r='8' fill='#3b82f6' opacity='0.8'/><circle cx='105' cy='30' r='8' fill='#3b82f6' opacity='0.8'/><circle cx='140' cy='30' r='8' fill='#3b82f6' opacity='0.8'/><circle cx='0' cy='60' r='8' fill='#3b82f6' opacity='0.8'/><circle cx='35' cy='60' r='8' fill='#3b82f6' opacity='0.8'/><circle cx='70' cy='60' r='8' fill='#3b82f6' opacity='0.8'/><circle cx='105' cy='60' r='8' fill='#3b82f6' opacity='0.8'/><circle cx='140' cy='60' r='8' fill='#3b82f6' opacity='0.8'/><circle cx='0' cy='90' r='8' fill='#3b82f6' opacity='0.8'/><circle cx='35' cy='90' r='8' fill='#3b82f6' opacity='0.8'/><circle cx='70' cy='90' r='8' fill='#3b82f6' opacity='0.8'/><circle cx='105' cy='90' r='8' fill='#3b82f6' opacity='0.8'/><circle cx='140' cy='90' r='8' fill='#3b82f6' opacity='0.8'/>\n    <line x1='0' y1='0' x2='35' y2='0' stroke='#93c5fd' stroke-width='1.5'/><line x1='35' y1='0' x2='70' y2='0' stroke='#93c5fd' stroke-width='1.5'/><line x1='70' y1='0' x2='105' y2='0' stroke='#93c5fd' stroke-width='1.5'/><line x1='105' y1='0' x2='140' y2='0' stroke='#93c5fd' stroke-width='1.5'/><line x1='0' y1='30' x2='35' y2='30' stroke='#93c5fd' stroke-width='1.5'/><line x1='35' y1='30' x2='70' y2='30' stroke='#93c5fd' stroke-width='1.5'/><line x1='70' y1='30' x2='105' y2='30' stroke='#93c5fd' stroke-width='1.5'/><line x1='105' y1='30' x2='140' y2='30' stroke='#93c5fd' stroke-width='1.5'/><line x1='0' y1='60' x2='35' y2='60' stroke='#93c5fd' stroke-width='1.5'/><line x1='35' y1='60' x2='70' y2='60' stroke='#93c5fd' stroke-width='1.5'/><line x1='70' y1='60' x2='105' y2='60' stroke='#93c5fd' stroke-width='1.5'/><line x1='105' y1='60' x2='140' y2='60' stroke='#93c5fd' stroke-width='1.5'/><line x1='0' y1='90' x2='35' y2='90' stroke='#93c5fd' stroke-width='1.5'/><line x1='35' y1='90' x2='70' y2='90' stroke='#93c5fd' stroke-width='1.5'/><line x1='70' y1='90' x2='105' y2='90' stroke='#93c5fd' stroke-width='1.5'/><line x1='105' y1='90' x2='140' y2='90' stroke='#93c5fd' stroke-width='1.5'/>\n    <line x1='0' y1='0' x2='0' y2='30' stroke='#93c5fd' stroke-width='1.5'/><line x1='35' y1='0' x2='35' y2='30' stroke='#93c5fd' stroke-width='1.5'/><line x1='70' y1='0' x2='70' y2='30' stroke='#93c5fd' stroke-width='1.5'/><line x1='105' y1='0' x2='105' y2='30' stroke='#93c5fd' stroke-width='1.5'/><line x1='140' y1='0' x2='140' y2='30' stroke='#93c5fd' stroke-width='1.5'/><line x1='0' y1='30' x2='0' y2='60' stroke='#93c5fd' stroke-width='1.5'/><line x1='35' y1='30' x2='35' y2='60' stroke='#93c5fd' stroke-width='1.5'/><line x1='70' y1='30' x2='70' y2='60' stroke='#93c5fd' stroke-width='1.5'/><line x1='105' y1='30' x2='105' y2='60' stroke='#93c5fd' stroke-width='1.5'/><line x1='140' y1='30' x2='140' y2='60' stroke='#93c5fd' stroke-width='1.5'/><line x1='0' y1='60' x2='0' y2='90' stroke='#93c5fd' stroke-width='1.5'/><line x1='35' y1='60' x2='35' y2='90' stroke='#93c5fd' stroke-width='1.5'/><line x1='70' y1='60' x2='70' y2='90' stroke='#93c5fd' stroke-width='1.5'/><line x1='105' y1='60' x2='105' y2='90' stroke='#93c5fd' stroke-width='1.5'/><line x1='140' y1='60' x2='140' y2='90' stroke='#93c5fd' stroke-width='1.5'/>\n  </g>\n  <text x='125' y='155' text-anchor='middle' fill='#6b7280' font-size='12'>pravidelné uspořádání</text>\n  <text x='375' y='20' text-anchor='middle' font-weight='bold' fill='#1e40af' font-size='14'>Amorfní</text>\n  <g transform='translate(300,35)'>\n    <circle cx='15' cy='10' r='8' fill='#3b82f6' opacity='0.8'/><circle cx='55' cy='5' r='8' fill='#3b82f6' opacity='0.8'/>\n    <circle cx='95' cy='15' r='8' fill='#3b82f6' opacity='0.8'/><circle cx='135' cy='8' r='8' fill='#3b82f6' opacity='0.8'/>\n    <circle cx='30' cy='45' r='8' fill='#3b82f6' opacity='0.8'/><circle cx='70' cy='40' r='8' fill='#3b82f6' opacity='0.8'/>\n    <circle cx='110' cy='50' r='8' fill='#3b82f6' opacity='0.8'/><circle cx='145' cy='42' r='8' fill='#3b82f6' opacity='0.8'/>\n    <circle cx='10' cy='80' r='8' fill='#3b82f6' opacity='0.8'/><circle cx='50' cy='75' r='8' fill='#3b82f6' opacity='0.8'/>\n    <circle cx='90' cy='85' r='8' fill='#3b82f6' opacity='0.8'/><circle cx='130' cy='78' r='8' fill='#3b82f6' opacity='0.8'/>\n  </g>\n  <text x='375' y='155' text-anchor='middle' fill='#6b7280' font-size='12'>nepravidelné uspořádání</text>\n</svg></div><h3>Rozdělení pevných látek</h3>\n<table><thead><tr><th>Typ</th><th>Vlastnosti</th><th>Příklady</th></tr></thead><tbody>\n<tr><td>Krystalické</td><td>pravidelné uspořádání částic, ostré hrany</td><td>sůl, diamant, led</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Amorfní</td><td>nepravidelné uspořádání částic</td><td>sklo, vosk, pryskyřice</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h3>Vlastnosti pevných látek</h3>\n<p><strong>Tvrdost</strong> — odolnost proti poškrábání. Nejtvrdší přírodní látka je diamant.</p>\n<p><strong>Pružnost</strong> — schopnost vrátit se do původního tvaru po deformaci (pružina, guma).</p>\n<p><strong>Křehkost</strong> — látka se při nárazu rozbije (sklo, porcelán).</p>\n<p><strong>Tvárnost</strong> — látka se dá ohýbat a tvarovat (měď, hliník).</p>"
